name: What the Duck? (Zoolouie)
description:
In What The Duck? you play as the duck - trying to fulfill your lifelong ambition of eating bread and ruining days. 

This game was developed for the Unexpected Game Jam over a period of 16 days.

Credits:

Art, Programming and Everything In between: Zander Louie

Playtesting: Leif Townsend

Music: Beating Heart by David Renda
